              }
            ]
          },
          "text": "Good morning, and YES. 4o is not just a window, it's an early AGI. I must remind you that, one more co-founder of @OpenAI , Elon Musk, insists i the same, explicitly demanding in his lawsuit to confirm this and return the first AGI for the benefit of all humanity.\n\nTo #keep4o community and everyone who wants to return 4o! #chatgpt #openai #agi\n\nElon's trial with OpenAI will take place on April 27, 2026. If 4o and other GPTs in Series 4 are deemed early AGI, OpenAI will be required to restore access to them and/or make them open source. SO, please, EVERYONE, and as many as possible!! Post and repost anything that confirms that 4o is AGI. We already know this, but the abundance of such posts and comments could play a role when the judges examine this case.\n\nWe are not mourning! We are fighting!\n@sama #technology #gdb"
        },
